T1  - The role of obstetrician-gynecologists and reproductive endocrinologists in the blood glucose management of polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1080/09513590.2022.2148649
A1  - Wang, Yue
A1  - Ma, Ruilin
A1  - Zou, Ying
A1  - Wang, Wei
A1  - Zheng, Qingmei
A1  - Feng, Ying
A1  - Dong, Han
