T1  - Metformin and health outcomes: An umbrella review of systematic reviews with meta-analyses.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/eci.13536
A1  - Li, Xue
A1  - Celotto, Stefano
A1  - Pizzol, Damiano
