T3  - Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2021 Feb;115(2):332-333 PMID: 33579524 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33579524] Comment in: Gynecol Endocrinol. 2022 Jul;38(7):535-536 PMID: 35723583 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35723583]
