T1  - The Pregnancy in Polycystic Ovary Syndrome II study: baseline characteristics and effects of obesity from a multicenter randomized clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2013.08.056
A1  - Legro, Richard S
A1  - Brzyski, Robert G
A1  - Diamond, Michael P
A1  - Coutifaris, Christos
A1  - Schlaff, William D
A1  - Alvero, Ruben
A1  - Casson, Peter
A1  - Christman, Gregory M
A1  - Huang, Hao
A1  - Yan, Qingshang
A1  - Haisenleder, Daniel J
A1  - Barnhart, Kurt T
A1  - Bates, G Wright
